{"calories":"820","carbs":76,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eThis rustic, French-inspired ragoût takes everything we love about earthy, meaty mushrooms and turns the volume way up. A trio of cremini, oyster, and shiitake mushrooms cooks down with shallots, garlic, and white wine until rich and concentrated. Spoon the gravy over creamy mascarpone grits and top with a fried egg for a bowl that’s wonderfully luxurious and comforting.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"4443a76de7","fat":42,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39001/lAyZEhCQl2D0VfaCvW1D_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39001/menu_small_lAyZEhCQl2D0VfaCvW1D_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39002/large_cropped_Is4NQXwwSHivNugCuHuX_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___MAIN_CROP.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39000/fBGGZqH3RGG1yesD2RYJ_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/hero_8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/menu_small_8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/small_square_8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/medium_square_8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/38999/recipe_profile_page_8vTHt4KQJ23deehsiQbA_Mushroom_Ragout_with_Cheesy_Grits___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}}],"name":"Mushroom Ragoût over Mascarpone-Parmesan Grits","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":25,"public_slug":"mushroom-ragout-with-cheesy-grits","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/23310/recipe_card20180119-9-k7lq53.pdf","recipe_id":3910,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Mushroom Ragoût","subtitle":"over Mascarpone-Parmesan Grits","title":"Mushroom Ragoût","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWiping mushrooms clean instead of rinsing prevents them from absorbing water. They won't brown well if they're too wet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpread the remaining mascarpone over toast or use as a dip for fruit. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe recommend rinsing the pot from the grits ASAP to make cleanup easier. Cooled grits can be a tough scrub!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["12\" large high-sided pan","6\" small pot with lid","10\" medium nonstick pan with lid"],"id":3910,"ingredients":["parsley","shallot","garlic","quick-cooking grits","grated Parmesan cheese","mascarpone cheese","unsalted butter","tomato paste","white wine","vegetable stock","thyme","cremini mushrooms","shiitake mushrooms","oyster mushrooms"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"parsley","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1279/medium_square_medium_square_parsley-test.jpg"},{"name":"shallot","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/130/medium_square_SHALLOT_copy.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"quick-cooking grits","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2024/medium_square_grain-grits.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"mascarpone cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1501/medium_square_MASCARPONE_CHEESE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"tomato paste","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/134/medium_square_TOMATO_PASTE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"vegetable stock","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/906/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_beef-broth.jpg"},{"name":"thyme","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1289/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"shiitake mushrooms","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/221/medium_square_shiitake-mushrooms-test.jpg"},{"name":"oyster mushrooms","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/609/medium_square_oyster-mushrooms.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","eggs","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"egg","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":16,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/274/medium_square_eggs-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":17,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":18,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39003/recipe_card_size_sgsGhkftTFawkG6dOuaG_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eRemove and discard \u003cstrong\u003emushroom\u003c/strong\u003e stems, then wipe caps clean with a damp paper towel and quarter (see recipe tip). Rinse \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e and roughly chop leaves, discarding stems. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eshallot \u003c/strong\u003eand mince. Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté mushrooms ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39004/recipe_card_size_EscbXsORfGMPHcvyozCi_2._Saute_Mushrooms.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat a large high-sided pan with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003eover medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring occasionally, until just golden, 6-8 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003eshallot\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e to pan and cook until softened, about 2 minutes more. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Remove pan from heat and set aside until Step 4.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook grits","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39006/recipe_card_size_8umFu8DASdaD0yeYULIW_4._Boil_Grits.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mushrooms cook, in a small pot, bring \u003cstrong\u003e4 cups water\u003c/strong\u003e to a near-boil over high heat (it should just be lightly bubbling). Whisk in \u003cstrong\u003egrits\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e until smooth. Reduce heat to medium low and cover. Cook, whisking occasionally, until thickened, 5-7 minutes. Remove pot from heat. Whisk in \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of mascarpone\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ebutter \u003c/strong\u003e(see recipe tip). Cover and set aside until Step 6.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Simmer mushroom ragoût","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39005/recipe_card_size_kq3XDQ7TTomqaTz0jEAJ_3._Simmer_Mushroom_Ragout.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eReturn pan with mushrooms to medium-high heat, then stir in \u003cstrong\u003etomato paste\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until combined, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ewine\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until reduced by half, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003estock \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003ewhole thyme sprigs \u003c/strong\u003eand bring to a boil over high heat, then reduce heat to low and simmer, stirring occasionally, until thickened, 6-8 minutes. Remove pan from heat and remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ewhole\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ethyme sprigs \u003c/strong\u003e(they've released all their flavor into the sauce).\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Fry eggs","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39007/recipe_card_size_8KKYl2UqQuq5ZfujZDqv_5._Fry_Eggs_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile ragoût simmers, heat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium nonstick pan over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, crack \u003cstrong\u003e2 eggs\u003c/strong\u003e into pan and season with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e. Fry until whites start to set, 2 minutes. Cover pan and continue frying until whites are mostly set but yolks are still runny, 2 minutes more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate mushroom ragoût and grits","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/39008/recipe_card_size_xLANFkSSTCeAsSOm5OrC_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eTaste \u003cstrong\u003emascarpone-Parmesan grits \u003c/strong\u003eand add \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired, then divide between shallow bowls (see recipe tip). Taste \u003cstrong\u003emushroom ragoût\u003c/strong\u003e and add \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired, then spoon over grits. Top with \u003cstrong\u003eeggs\u003c/strong\u003e, garnish with \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e, and dig in! \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Egg","slug":"egg","hex_color":""},{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}